WEBVTT

00:01.180 --> 00:03.520
[bird calling]

00:03.590 --> 00:06.020
[slow-paced music]

00:06.090 --> 00:08.020
♪♪♪

00:08.090 --> 00:10.030
[distant cheering and applause]

00:15.870 --> 00:17.870
[drumming]

00:17.930 --> 00:19.800
- [girl]: Give me an I!
- [spectators]: I!

00:19.870 --> 00:21.740
- [girl]: Give me an L!
- [spectators]: L!

00:21.810 --> 00:23.840
- [girl]: Another L!
- [spectators]: L!

00:23.910 --> 00:26.470
- [girl]: W!
- [spectators]: W!
- Give me an O!

00:26.540 --> 00:29.380
- [spectators]: O!
- Give me an O!
- [all]: O!

00:29.380 --> 00:32.950
- [girl]: Give me a D!
- [spectators]: D!
- Millwood! Woo! Woo!

00:32.950 --> 00:34.950
[cheering and whistling]

00:34.950 --> 00:37.490
[applause]

00:41.890 --> 00:43.690
- Mayor Shepard.

00:43.760 --> 00:46.230
Wanna make a friendly wager
on the game?

00:46.300 --> 00:48.200
- I'm a public servant, Ben.

00:48.260 --> 00:51.170
Betting on the home team would
be violating some sort of oath.

00:51.170 --> 00:54.340
But I'm gonna say
Bulldogs in penalty kicks.

00:57.210 --> 00:59.110
- They're here.

00:59.180 --> 01:01.080
[cheering and whistling]

01:05.780 --> 01:07.620
- How you holding up?
- I don't know

01:07.680 --> 01:09.480
- if I'm going to get through it.
- I'm not supposed

01:09.550 --> 01:11.650
to say anything but... there's

01:11.660 --> 01:14.660
- a scout here from McGill.
- For Molly?

01:14.660 --> 01:16.820
- The kid's a rising star.

01:16.890 --> 01:19.330
You must be a proud uncle.

01:19.400 --> 01:21.400
- Could not be prouder.

01:21.400 --> 01:23.670
- OK, guys! Bring it in!

01:26.000 --> 01:27.770
The only thing that stands

01:27.840 --> 01:29.600
between us and playoffs
is one game.

01:29.670 --> 01:31.840
You guys ready? Let's do this.

01:31.840 --> 01:35.280
- Bring it in. Three, two one.
- [all]: Bulldogs Fight!

01:35.280 --> 01:37.680
[cheering]

01:37.750 --> 01:39.510
[sharp intake of breath]

01:43.620 --> 01:46.450
- Woo! [whistle blowing]

01:48.690 --> 01:51.560
- Go!
- [man]: Down the line,

01:51.630 --> 01:54.180
Molly! Down the line!
- Pass it! Pass it!

01:54.205 --> 01:55.054
[girl]: Go Molly!

01:55.100 --> 01:57.800
[girl]: Bulldogs!
Come on! Let's go, Dogs!

02:01.100 --> 02:04.140
- Millway! Woo!
- [cheering and whistling]

02:06.110 --> 02:08.610
[whistle blowing]

02:11.050 --> 02:13.710
[booing]

02:13.780 --> 02:15.580
- Ref, Ref, Ref!

02:15.650 --> 02:17.720
- Yellow card.
That's gotta hurt.

02:17.790 --> 02:20.190
- You're welcome
to take over anytime.

02:20.260 --> 02:22.620
- That's not my job.
- You're right,

02:22.690 --> 02:25.530
it's not. Aren't you supposed
to be encouraging people?

02:25.600 --> 02:27.700
- I'm not here to coddle you.

02:27.760 --> 02:30.000
You're gonna score today.

02:30.070 --> 02:31.870
I can tell.

02:33.900 --> 02:35.670
[sighing]

02:37.570 --> 02:40.410
- [woman]: Go Bulldogs!
- [whistle blowing]

02:40.480 --> 02:43.340
- Get 'em up, Bulldogs!
Go, Bulldogs! Go long!

02:43.410 --> 02:45.180
[cheering]

02:53.520 --> 02:55.420
- YEAH!

02:58.330 --> 03:00.760
- Go Molly! Woohoo!

03:00.760 --> 03:02.660
[marching band music]

03:02.730 --> 03:05.200
♪♪♪

