09:50.640 --> 09:53.370
- ♪♪ Feel, feel it grow ♪

09:53.380 --> 09:55.440
♪ In your mind ♪

09:55.450 --> 09:58.980
♪ In your mind ♪

09:59.050 --> 10:03.920
♪ Life is how you live it ♪

10:03.920 --> 10:07.190
♪ Through time, through time ♪

10:07.260 --> 10:09.890
♪ And there's no desert sun ♪

10:09.960 --> 10:11.890
♪ That is hot enough ♪

10:11.960 --> 10:15.900
♪ To feed your fire ♪

10:15.960 --> 10:19.200
♪ We're shipwrecked like fools ♪

10:19.270 --> 10:23.940
♪ Only to become
the ocean's choir ♪

10:23.940 --> 10:26.340
