- ♪ I'm not ♪

42:09.710 --> 42:13.150
♪ Just dragging my heels ♪

42:15.780 --> 42:19.180
♪ I'm not toeing the line ♪

42:19.190 --> 42:25.260
♪ I'd stop thinking
about counting ♪

42:25.330 --> 42:29.800
